OL,3,CBoy's epileptic seizures 'cured' by
OL,4,Cpioneering brain surgery
OL,6,F*WARNING: This report contains footage
OL,7,Fof live neurosurgery*
OL,9,FA Somerset boy who suffered from
OL,10,Ffrequent epileptic seizures has been
OL,11,F"cured" by pioneering neurosurgery in
OL,12,FBristol.
OL,14,FFor Finley, seizures were as much a
OL,15,Fpart of life as getting dressed and
OL,16,Fgoing to school.
OL,18,FThe six-year-old from Burnham-on-Sea
OL,19,Fis one of 600,000 people in the UK
OL,20,Fliving with epilepsy. Or at least, he
OL,21,Fwas.
