OL,3,CBoy's epileptic seizures 'cured' by
OL,4,Cpioneering brain surgery
OL,6,FSince having brain surgery at Bristol
OL,7,FChildren's Hospital six months ago,
OL,8,FFinley hasn't had a single seizure.
OL,9,FHis 'incurable' condition appears to
OL,10,Fhave been cured.
OL,12,F"It's absolutely amazing," said
OL,13,FFinley's mother, Sarah. "When we first
OL,14,Fstarted out, we never thought he would
OL,15,Fbe seizure-free. We thought that was
OL,16,Four life now."
OL,18,FBristol Children's Hospital is one of
OL,19,Ffour centres in the UK able to carry
OL,20,Fout this type of operation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
