OL,3,CBoy's epileptic seizures 'cured' by
OL,4,Cpioneering brain surgery
OL,6,FFor generations, the only only option
OL,7,Fwas medication to reduce seizures,
OL,8,Frather than cure them completely.
OL,10,FThat's why this treatment at Bristol
OL,11,Fcould be so exciting for young
OL,12,Fpatients, with decades of life ahead
OL,13,Fof them.
OL,15,FI asked Finley what he thought about
OL,16,Fbeing seizure-free. "Good", he replied.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
